# 1. Ignore everything
*

# 2. Now, create exceptions to un-ignore specific files/folders.
# The '!' character negates a pattern.

# Un-ignore the .gitignore file itself so it gets committed.
!.gitignore

# Un-ignore the parent folder to allow Git to see inside it.
!Assets/Game/
!Assets/Resources/

# Un-ignore your target folder and everything inside it.
!Assets/Game/Scripts/
!Assets/Game/Scripts/**
!Assets/Resources/
!Assets/Resources/**